      "rationale": "All model inputs (geometry, boundary conditions, fluid properties, and hemolysis model coefficients) are traceable to documented sources. Pump geometry was derived from FDA-published CAD files. Fluid properties are from ISO 10993-4 compliant blood analog specifications. Hemolysis model coefficients are from Giersiepen et al. (1990) as cited in FDA guidance. Input uncertainty ranges are documented and propagated through the sensitivity analysis.",
